I submitted my ad for review I want to say on April 21st and it has still not been reviewed. Could I have this ad reviewed?

I'm sorry to hear that your ad hasn't been reviewed yet. If your account is new and hasn't been verified, this might be causing the delay. To proceed with the verification process and have your account approved, please provide the following details by emailing adsupport@newsbreak.com with the subject line: Business Verification –
- Company's full address
- Company's legal entity name
- Company's EHID or DUNS number
- Primary contact person's name
- Company's phone number
Once we receive this information, we will conduct a thorough review and update you on your account status. We appreciate your cooperation in maintaining a secure and compliant advertising environment for all our partners.
is EHID the same as my EIN?

EHID and EIN are not the same. EHID stands for Employer Health Insurance Data, while EIN stands for Employer Identification Number, which is used for tax purposes. If you need more information on how these identifiers are used in the context of NewsBreak, feel free to ask!
